{"type":"message","id":"d69d72f6","parentId":"cc356d8d","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:30:00.069Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:321d856c-eb47-44d0-a1de-24fd64d31f4f 盘后复盘+邮件报告] 执行每日盘后复盘流程：\n1. SCP 从云服务器拉取 E:/Quant/Datas/daily_result.json 和 E:/Quant/Datas/positions.json\n2. 读今天的 plan.json（对比预测 vs 实际）\n3. 读历史报告索引 _index.json（防止重复犯错）\n4. 量化团队全員复盘：\n   - 今日盈亏是多少？每只股票表现如何？\n   - 哪些因子对了？哪些因子错了？\n5. **因子有效性追踪**（重要）：\n   - 读 strategies/reports/factor_tracking.json\n   - 对比今日每只股票的选股因子（PE/PB分位、机构资金流向、ROE趋势、换手率异动等）\n   - 判断哪些因子与正收益相关、哪些因子失效\n   - 更新 factor_tracking.json：更新各因子的 days_above/days_below、avg_return_when_signal、hit_rate，追加 notes\n   - 保存更新后的 factor_tracking.json\n   - 在报告中输出因子有效性排行榜：最有效因子 TOP3 + 最失效因子 TOP3\n6. **新闻回溯**（个股异常时触发）：\n   - 如果某只持仓股当日涨跌幅 > 5% 或触发止损/止盈，搜索该股票当日相关新闻\n   - 用 web_search 搜索 \"股票代码/名称 + 新闻\" 和所属行业相关新闻\n   - 分析新闻是否为涨跌原因，记录到因子追踪的 notes 中\n   - 如果是突发利空/利好导致止损/止盈，标注为「新闻驱动」类型\n7. 生成 Markdown 复盘报告，包含：\n   - 今日盈亏总览\n   - 个股表现明细（异常个股附新闻回溯）\n   - 因子有效性分析（排行榜）\n   - 教训总结（对比 _index.json 防重复）\n   - 明日关注点\n8. 用 Gmail SMTP 发邮件到 l1cheeyuan@163.com\n   - 发件箱: yuanlynch@gmail.com\n   - App Password: jsnjyjwpavymplev\n   - SMTP: smtp.gmail.com:587, STARTTLS\n   - 参考脚本: /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace/send_morning_report.py\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 31st, 2026 — 18:30 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-31 10:30 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774953000068}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bc104c6","parentId":"d69d72f6","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:30:32.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nThis is a cron job task that requires me to execute a daily post-market review process. Let me break down what needs to be done:\n\n1. SCP from cloud server to pull daily_result.json and positions.json\n2. Read today's plan.json (compare predictions vs actual)\n3. Read historical report index _index.json\n4. Quantitative team review:\n   - Today's profit/loss, stock performance\n   - Which factors were right/wrong\n5. Factor effectiveness tracking:\n   - Read strategies/reports/factor_tracking.json\n   - Compare today's stock selection factors\n   - Update factor_tracking.json with statistics\n   - Generate factor effectiveness rankings\n6. News retrospective (for stocks with >5% movement or stop-loss/take-profit)\n7. Generate Markdown review report\n8. Send email via Gmail SMTP\n\nLet me start by checking the current directory structure and then proceed step by step.\n\nFirst, I need to check if the necessary files exist and understand the current setup.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n我将执行每日盘后复盘流程。让我先检查当前工作目录和必要的文件结构。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e383908564af4cb89ee9d1d4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pwd && ls -la"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":33554,"output":242,"cacheRead":7527,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41323,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774953000068}}
