{"type":"message","id":"99f143cf","parentId":"2e609966","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:31:34.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nNow I have a better understanding of the situation. The trading system has been experiencing import errors with 'xtdata' from 'xtquant.xtdata', which is preventing the system from running properly. This explains why:\n\n1. The plan shows positions should have been taken\n2. But the positions.json shows no positions were actually held\n3. The daily_result.json shows the same error\n\nSince I can't connect to the cloud server due to SSH issues, I'll proceed with the data I have available. Let me now start the post-market review process with the available information.\n\nLet me create a comprehensive post-market review report based on the available data, and then look at the memory files to see if there are any patterns or lessons learned.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6659d06bea4d4df88da4346d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":116,"output":181,"cacheRead":47887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774953088065}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb9529b5","parentId":"99f143cf","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:31:34.857Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6659d06bea4d4df88da4346d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - 柴荣的量化交易经验总结\n\n## 🚫 操作红线（必须遵守）\n\n### 交易概念红线\n- **开盘涨幅 ≠ 实际收益**：+6.47% 是相对前收盘价的变化，以开盘价买入成本就在高位，盈亏取决于之后走势\n- **T+1**：买入当天绝对不能卖出\n- **涨跌幅限制的是委托价**：实际涨幅可以小于限制值\n- 涉及交易决策时，先查阅 `A_STOCK_RULES.md`\n\n## 🚫 操作红线（必须遵守）\n\n### 代码修改权限\n- **MyQuant 项目代码（`/Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant/`）绝对不能擅自修改**\n- 如需改代码，必须先向 Lynch 报告问题、说明修改方案，等他确认同意后才能动\n- **违规记录**：2026-03-26 未获授权修改了 `tushare_client.py`（`src=\"SW\"` → `\"SW2014\"` 和代理绕过 patch），已遭批评\n\n### 可直接修改的文件（不需要确认）\n- Clash/代理配置文件（`~/.config/clash/`、`~/Library/Application Support/mihomo-party/`）\n- workspace-chairong 下的文件（`~/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/`）\n- MEMORY.md 等记忆文件\n\n---\n\n## 教训总结\n\n### 2026-03-06 数据源问题\n\n**问题**：使用Yahoo Finance获取紫金矿业(601899)历史数据时，数据严重错误\n- 错误显示2025年价格约17元\n- 实际2026年价格约35-44元\n\n**原因**：Yahoo Finance对中国A股支持不完善，可能未正确处理复权或代码映射\n\n**解决方案**：\n- ✅ 使用 **iFinD (同花顺)** 获取A股数据 - 数据准确\n- ❌ **Finnhub** 主要支持美股，对A股支持有限（测试显示403权限错误）\n- ❌ **Yahoo Finance** 数据不准确\n\n---\n\n## 工具选择规则\n\n### 查A股（沪深）\n- ✅ **首选1：Baostock** - 完全免费，数据准确，实时+历史+财务全覆盖，成功率100%\n- ✅ **首选2：Tushare（基础接口）** - 需Token，部分接口需积分，成功率70%\n- ⚠️ **备选：iFinD (ths_ifind)** - 同花顺数据，需付费\n- ❌ **不用akshare** - 因Clash VPN拦截无法使用\n- ❌ 不用 Yahoo Finance - 数据有严重错误\n- ❌ 不用 finnhub - 不支持A股（返回403）\n\n### 查美股\n- ✅ **首选1：Finnhub** - 实时行情、公司基本面、财务指标\n- ✅ **首选2：Alpha Vantage** - 历史K线、技术指标\n- ✅ **备用：Tiingo、EODHD**\n\n### 查大宗商品（黄金、铜）\n- ✅ **首选：Alpha Vantage** - 黄金、铜等大宗商品数据准确\n- ✅ **备用：QVeris Finance Gold Aggregation**\n\n---\n\n## 紫金矿业最新数据 (2026-03-06)\n\n| 日期 | 收盘价 | 备注 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| 2026-01-05 | 35.40 | 年初 |\n| 2026-01-29 | 43.45 | 月度高点 |\n| 2026-02-02 | 36.61 | 回调低点 |\n| 2026-03-02 | 40.77 | 近期高点 |\n| 2026-03-05 | 37.67 | 昨日收盘 |\n| 2026-03-06 | 36.33 | 今日当前 |\n\n**结论**：2026年以来最低价36.27元（2月2日），从未跌破30元\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774953094855}}
