{"type":"message","id":"124ed36e","parentId":"9cc19449","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:31:39.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nPerfect! There are recent memory files from each day. Let me read the most recent ones to understand what's been happening and check for patterns.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_75a08bd738064ebcaaa147c8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-03-31.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":234,"output":54,"cacheRead":49151,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49439,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774953097679}}
{"type":"message","id":"598cf639","parentId":"124ed36e","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:31:39.973Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_75a08bd738064ebcaaa147c8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-31 记忆\n\n## 3月30日（周一）实盘复盘\n\n### 执行状态：失败\n- QMT 没有执行任何交易（持仓为空，可用资金 1000 万没动）\n- 原因：Windows 定时任务 09:15 触发时与已有实例冲突（0x800710E0）\n- Lynch 10:33 手动跑了一次，但已错过最佳买入时机\n- 已通过 SSH PowerShell 将 MultipleInstances 改为 1（停止现有实例）\n\n### plan.json 选股表现\n| 股票 | 30日日涨跌 | 开盘买入→收盘 |\n|:--|:--|:--|\n| 宁波能源 600982 | **-9.93%**（差点跌停） | -6.76% |\n| 瑞丰银行 601528 | -0.93% | +0.19% |\n| 信邦制药 002664 | -3.86% | +2.21% |\n| 中国铝业 601600（用户关注） | +4.63% | -0.25%（高开低走） |\n| 云铝股份 000807（用户关注） | +9.50% | +1.42% |\n\n### 关键教训\n1. **涨停板次日选股是坑**：宁波能源 3/27 涨停（+10%），3/30 差点跌停（-9.93%）。preopen 没过滤\"昨日涨停\"股，需要加过滤规则\n2. **高开追涨风险大**：中国铝业高开 4.8%，收盘只涨 4.6%，追进去微亏\n3. **大盘抗跌但个股分化**：上证 +0.24%（低开高走），但个股亏的不少\n\n### 大盘环境\n- 上证 +0.24%（收 3923），成交额 8398 亿（放量）\n- 外盘大跌日 A 股相对抗跌，中东战争持续\n\n---\n\n## SSH 连接方式确认\n- **paramiko 可用**，密码从 `openclaw.json` env.SSH_PASSWORD 获取\n- QMT 路径：`E:\\国金证券QMT交易端`，xtquant 在 bin.x64 目录\n- 系统没有独立 python.exe，需要通过 QMT 客户端或 IDE 连接账户\n- positions.json 路径：`E:\\Quant\\Datas\\positions.json`\n- plan.json 路径：`E:\\Quant\\strategies\\plan.json`（已修正，之前写的 C:/PTrade 是旧路径）\n\n## 盘后 cron 状态\n- UUID: `321d856c-eb47-44d0-a1de-24fd64d31f4f`\n- 3/30 18:30 触发但被 aborted，未完成复盘报告\n- 原因待查\n\n## A_STOCK_RULES.md 已创建\n- 路径：`/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/A_STOCK_RULES.md`\n- 覆盖 11 个章节：交易时间、单位、涨跌幅、集合竞价、连续竞价、T+1、费用、停牌、指数、术语、Agent 误区\n- MEMORY.md 已添加交易概念红线引用\n\n## 待办\n- [ ] quant_params 加\"昨日涨停\"过滤（避免选涨停板次日股票）\n- [ ] 检查盘后 cron 为什么被 aborted\n- [ ] 确认 Windows 定时任务修复后明天能正常触发\n- [ ] 等用户确认 quant_params V3 的 4 个参数修改\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774953099971}}
