{"type":"message","id":"29e24994","parentId":"12dbe5fa","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:31:46.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nThat file doesn't exist. Let me check the memory files that do exist.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_200e08b48b594bfab1c15511","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-03-29.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":59,"output":41,"cacheRead":50315,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50415,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774953103508}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e21aab6","parentId":"29e24994","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:31:46.697Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_200e08b48b594bfab1c15511","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-29 回测引擎开发 & 历史数据回放\n\n## 回测引擎 V4 完成（Baostock 版）\n\n### 关键修复历程\n1. **Tushare 太慢（4-6s/次）** → 换成 Baostock（秒级完成）\n2. **日期格式 bug**：Baostock 返回 `2026-03-19`（带横线），缓存 key 存了原始格式而非 `20260319`，导致 `get_bar` 永远匹配不上 → `data[row[0]]` 改为 `data[d]`（d 已 replace 横线）\n3. **`_fmt()` 插入吞掉了 `def preload_all`** → 手动补回\n4. **交易日历过滤逻辑 bug**：`row[1] == '1' and row[0] >= sd[0] if sd else True` 运算符优先级错误 → 简化为先全收集再转格式\n\n### 最终脚本\n- 路径：`strategies/backtest/backtest_engine.py`（V4，Baostock 数据源）\n- 支持单次回测和网格搜索（`--mode grid`）\n- 正确 T+1 逻辑：买入当天不能卖出\n- 止损止盈用 close 价，rebalance 卖出用 open 价\n- 手续费：佣金万0.845 + 印花税千1 + 沪市过户费十万分之1\n\n## batch_preopen 完成\n\n- 路径：`strategies/backtest/batch_preopen.py`\n- 129 天全部成功（0 失败），平均 7.8s/天\n- 超时设为 300s（5分钟），足够覆盖 Tushare 慢响应\n- 输出目录：`/Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant/outputs/preopen/YYYYMMDD/`\n\n## 网格搜索结果（135 个 BUY_ALLOWED 信号日，199 笔交易）\n\n### 最优参数\n| 参数 | 最优值 |\n|:--|:--|\n| stop_loss | **3%** |\n| take_profit | **20%** |\n| max_hold | **3 天** |\n| top_n | **3 只** |\n\n### 最优表现\n- 胜率 46.7%，总收益 +6.56%，夏普 3.70，最大回撤 8.42%\n- 止盈触发 8 次，平均 +19.8%\n- 114 次 rebalance（每天换仓频繁）\n\n### 关键发现\n1. **tn=3 vs tn=5 差距巨大**：tn=3 所有组合都远好于 tn=5（差距 30-60 百分点），第 4-5 只股票是负贡献\n2. **选股高度集中**：199 笔交易只在 ~10 只股票循环（融捷股份、华电辽能、云煤能源、湖南发展、天际股份），行业只有 电力设备/公用事业/煤炭\n3. **止损越紧越好（3%）**：快速止损减少亏损\n4. **止盈放开（20%）**：让利润跑，不被 rebalance 过早踢掉\n5. **alpha 衰减快（3 天）**：持仓超 3 天收益下降\n\n### 风险提示\n- 7 个月数据、高度集中的选股池，结论可靠性有限\n- 选股集中在 3 个行业，可能是 preopen 因子偏好问题（需 Trae 排查）\n\n## Tushare 频率确认\n- 5000 积分 = 500 次/分钟（非之前以为的 200 次）\n- 但从 exec/conda 环境调用 Tushare 仍需 4-6s/次（网络/代理问题）\n- 回测引擎已用 Baostock 绕过此问题\n\n## Baostock 注意事项\n- 日期参数必须用 `YYYY-MM-DD` 格式\n- 返回数据的 date 字段也是 `YYYY-MM-DD` 格式，需 replace 横线转 `YYYYMMDD`\n- `query_history_k_data_plus` 的 adjustflag=\"2\" 是前复权\n- 免费、无频率限制、速度稳定\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774953106692}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d2e9d60","parentId":"1e21aab6","timestamp":"2026-03-31T10:31:54.768Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the situation. Let me summarize what I've learned:\n\n1. **Current Status**: The trading system has been experiencing technical issues with the xtdata import from xtquant.xtdata, preventing any trades from being executed.\n\n2. **Plan vs Actual**: \n   - Plan called for 5 positions (新能泰山, 宁波能源, 石大胜华, 融捷股份, 江钨装备)\n   - No positions were actually taken due to system errors\n   - Available cash remains at 100,002.36 yuan\n\n3. **Recent Issues**:\n   - March 30: System error prevented execution, missed trading opportunities\n   - Several stocks in the plan performed poorly (e.g., 宁波能源 -9.93%)\n   - Technical issues with Windows scheduled tasks and multiple instances\n\n4. **Factor Tracking**: The system is set up to track factor effectiveness but hasn't been collecting data due to the technical issues.\n\n5. **Key Learnings**: There are important lessons about avoiding stocks that hit limit-ups the previous day, avoiding high-chase entries, etc.\n\nNow I'll proceed with creating the post-market review report based on this data.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n基于收集到的数据，我现在开始执行每日盘后复盘流程。由于交易系统存在技术问题，实际没有产生交易，我将基于可用的数据进行分析。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4a8bff76bf9d43cd9a431a4b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://api.tavily.com/search?q=A股今日行情%202026年3月31日&api_key=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\" | jq -r '.results[] | \"\\(.title): \\(.snippet)\"' | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":946,"output":388,"cacheRead":50414,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51748,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774953106697}}
